ull, "text": "Re Eve: 迟交作业很多老师都是迟一天少10%，20%的分", "timestamp": 1614311272, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1145554, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 226500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 要扣分也是合理的，但对比起来差距就很大", "timestamp": 1614311308, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1145557, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 226500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 大物实验并没准备让同学学会什么东西", "timestamp": 1614311334, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1145563, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 226500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 害，屁用没有的课多了去了", "timestamp": 1614311426, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1145603, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 226500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "补做为什么不扣分，别人都能做完的事情要是补做不扣分有失公平", "timestamp": 1614311787, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1145606, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 226500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "而且补做也说明预习有问题，这么算也要扣", "timestamp": 1614311830, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1146094, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 226500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 听到这种言论我就无语，我现在大二能把专业课修完拿4.0是不是说明清华大部分都是废物？老师搞的不是教学而是考核合理吗？屑课就是屑课有什么好辩驳的？", "timestamp": 1614316961, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1299796, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 226500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 可是有些仪器是坏的呀（捂脸）cz上学期就有碰到。。。那重做就和预习没关系了…", "timestamp": 1616223480, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1355432, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 226500, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "只有一个5分会挂吗？\n", "timestamp": 1617017526, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 13, "pid": 226500, "reply": 17, "tag": null, "text": "物理实验课扣分项重申-请大家注意\n1. 课上抄袭、课后报告雷同：依情节扣分直至0分\n\n2. 不预习：-1\n\n3. 课上未完成实验任务而课后补做的：按内容量扣分\n\n4. 实验结束没有整理仪器：成绩降档\n\n5. 报告格式不符合要求（如格式、字数）：成绩降1档或更多\n\n6. 报告迟交：实验后四周内未交，不记报告分（晚交一周大约扣1分，报告分扣完为止）\n\n我直接吐了，一个屑课怎么要求这么jb多？课上做不完补做为什么都要扣分？", "timestamp": 1614310769, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1617017525, "url": "", "vote": {}}}